title: Cosmic Queries: Comets and Asteroids with Dr. Amy Mainzer
description: Curious about comets? Anxious about near-Earth asteroids? Join us as guest host Dr. Amy Mainzer from NASA/JPL answers your Cosmic Queries with a little help from comic co-host Chuck Nice.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
